pageContext.claim: “There was one case where we had a tremendous snowstorm, and it was just about frozen. It was like a monster storm, I don't even know how I got there. I said, "How's the crowd?" "It's just not full, sir." I said what does that mean. There's like two seats on top. Thousands and thousands of people couldn't get there. So they show pictures of the empty seats.”
pageContext.analysis: There's no evidence that this ever occured. There are often empty seats at Trump rallies.
